			<div class="content" id="post-content-3321766">
									

<p>also, let's see, the 'black vault' is from the <a href="http://collection.hht.net.au/firsthhtpictures/fullRecordPicture.jsp?recnoListAttr=recnoList&amp;recno=32219">New South Wales Police Department</a>, &quot;Commercial interior showing damaged safes. Details unknown, late 1930s&quot;. &quot;Justice &amp; Police Museum ; 193&quot;</p>
